'''Daysong''' was a splinter group of the [[Rights of Sentience Party]] which advocated in [[13 ABY/Legends|13 ABY]] that the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[Chief of State (New Republic)/Legends|Chief of State]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo's]] [[Noghri/Legends|Noghri]] honor guard was a form of humiliation for the already long-suffering species and that they should be replaced by [[Droid/Legends|droids]]. They also objected to [[synthdroid]]s as guards on the grounds that [[Synthflesh/Legends|synthflesh]] was alive and had rights as well.

